  "description": "The image showcases a breathtaking view of the night sky, dominated by the Milky Way galaxy stretching across the frame.  The galactic core appears as a bright, densely packed band of stars, contrasted against the darker, more sparsely populated areas of space. Numerous stars, varying in brightness, are scattered throughout the dark canvas, creating a sense of immense depth and scale. The stars appear as tiny points of light, some with a slight halo effect, while the Milky Way's band presents a more diffuse, cloud-like texture. There are subtle gradients in the darkness, suggesting the vastness of interstellar space.",
